arguments.template:
<mat-tab-group>
  <mat-tab *ngFor="let tab of option.tabitems; let i=index;"
    label="{{ tab.title | mk_ng2_i18n: page.pageID }}">
    <jsf-root *ngFor="let widget of tab.items"
      fxFlex="{{widget.flex}}"
      [widgets]="widgets"
      [debug]="debug"
      [innerOption]="innerOption"
      [parentGroup]="parentGroup"
      [page]="page"
      [schema]="schema"
      [master]="master"
      [data]="data"
      [option]="widget"
      [direction]="direction"
      [num]="num"
      [index]="index"
      [dimension]="dimension"
      (buttonClick)="buttonClicked($event)">
    </jsf-root>
  </mat-tab>
</mat-tab-group>
